PENDULUM
The reward function gives a high score when the pendulum is close to being upright.

CARTPOLE-BALANCING
The reward function gives a high score when the pole is close to being upright as much as possible without fall.

CARTPOLE-SWINGUP
The reward function gives a high score when the pendulum is close to being upright with the cart at zero position.

FLYER2D
Reward the agent for achieving the goal state within a minimum time frame and then stabilize there.
